The Premier League makes a return this weekend, after Carabao Cup fixtures in midweek. Table toppers Liverpool are away to Sheffield United in Saturday’s early kick-off. Chelsea welcome Brighton to Stamford Bridge and Tottenham Hotspur host Southampton. The late kick off will see champions Manchester City travel to Everton. Saturday, September 28
FT: Sheffield United 0 vs Liverpool 1
